---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="为什么选择Geppetto而非传统平台 | 智能制造新时代" description="深度对比传统制造平台与Geppetto AI驱动制造的核心差异，了解为什么越来越多企业选择智能制造新模式">

<div class="min-h-screen bg-white">
  <!-- Hero区域 -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          传统制造平台 vs<br/>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">AI智能制造</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          为什么越来越多的企业选择Geppetto，告别传统制造平台的局限性，拥抱AI驱动的制造新时代
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl px-6 py-4">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-300">50%+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">成本节省</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl px-6 py-4">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-300">10倍</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">报价速度</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl px-6 py-4">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-300">±0.03mm</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">实际精度</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 核心差异概览 -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
          🚀 制造模式革命性差异
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          从传统外包到AI智能制造，这不仅仅是技术升级，更是商业模式的颠覆
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- 传统平台模式 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 border-2 border-gray-200">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gray-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">🏭</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">传统制造平台</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">依赖人工报价和供应商网络</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 mt-1">❌</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">报价慢且不透明</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">人工报价需要3-7天，过程不透明</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 mt-1">❌</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">质量参差不齐</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">依赖不同供应商，质量难以统一保证</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 mt-1">❌</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">价格缺乏竞争力</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">多层中间商，成本层层加码</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 mt-1">❌</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">交付周期不确定</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">供应商排期不透明，交付时间难预测</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-500 mr-3 mt-1">❌</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">MOQ限制严格</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">最小订单量要求高，小批量成本昂贵</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Geppetto模式 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-blue-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 border-2 border-purple-200">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">🤖</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Geppetto AI制造</h3>
            <p class="text-purple-600">AI驱动的智能制造新模式</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">✅</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">AI秒级智能报价</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">AI分析CAD文件，30秒内生成精准报价</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">✅</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">±0.03mm超高精度</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">AI优化工艺，实际精度超越承诺40%</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">✅</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">成本降低50%+</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">去中间商化，AI优化成本结构</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">✅</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">24小时极速交付</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">学徒制造模式，专门产能保障</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">✅</span>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-gray-800">单件起做无MOQ</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">批量价格做单件，不设最小订单量</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 详细对比表格 -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
          📊 全方位能力对比
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          数据说话，一目了然的差异化优势
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 对比表格 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border border-gray-200">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full">
            <thead class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-white">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-lg font-semibold">对比维度</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-lg font-semibold">传统制造平台</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-lg font-semibold">国际主流平台</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-lg font-semibold bg-yellow-500/20">Geppetto</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <!-- 报价速度 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">⚡ 报价速度</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">3-7天</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">1-3天</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">30秒</td>
              </tr>
              
              <!-- 报价准确性 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-gray-25">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">🎯 报价准确性</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">70-80%</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">80-85%</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">95%+</td>
              </tr>
              
              <!-- 制造精度 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">📐 制造精度</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">±0.1mm</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">±0.05mm</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">±0.03mm</td>
              </tr>
              
              <!-- 交付时间 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-gray-25">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">🚀 交付时间</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">7-15天</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">3-10天</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">24小时</td>
              </tr>
              
              <!-- 价格优势 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">💰 价格优势</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">基准价格</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">溢价10-20%</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">节省50%+</td>
              </tr>
              
              <!-- 最小订单量 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-gray-25">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">📦 最小订单量</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">50-100件</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">1-10件</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">1件起做</td>
              </tr>
              
              <!-- 质量保证 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">🛡️ 质量保证</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">供应商保证</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">平台担保</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">AI+专家双重保证</td>
              </tr>
              
              <!-- 客户服务 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-gray-25">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">🎧 客户服务</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">工作时间</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">24小时邮件</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">24/7即时响应</td>
              </tr>
              
              <!-- 技术支持 -->
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-800">🔧 技术支持</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">基础支持</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">工程师支持</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-green-600">AI+专家团队</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 核心技术差异 -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-blue-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
          🧠 核心技术差异
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          AI技术革命如何重新定义制造服务
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- AI报价引擎 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">🤖</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">AI智能报价引擎</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-3">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-red-800 mb-1">传统模式</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-red-600">人工看图报价，经验依赖性强，准确性70-80%</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-3">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 mb-1">Geppetto优势</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-green-600">AI深度学习，自动识别几何特征，报价准确性95%+</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">10倍</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">报价速度提升</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 智能工艺规划 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-100 to-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">⚙️</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">智能工艺规划</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-3">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-red-800 mb-1">传统模式</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-red-600">工程师手工规划，效率低，精度依赖经验</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-3">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 mb-1">Geppetto优势</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-green-600">AI优化加工路径，预测热变形，自动补偿误差</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">40%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">精度提升</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 质量预测控制 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-100 to-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">🔍</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">质量预测控制</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-3">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-red-800 mb-1">传统模式</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-red-600">事后检测，问题发现晚，返工成本高</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-3">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 mb-1">Geppetto优势</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-green-600">AI实时监控，预测质量风险，主动预防缺陷</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600">90%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">缺陷预防率</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 成本结构分析 -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
          💰 成本结构透明化分析
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          为什么Geppetto能做到50%成本节省
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- 传统平台成本结构 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-3xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">传统平台成本结构</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">制造成本</span>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 mr-3">
                  <div class="bg-blue-500 h-3 rounded-full" style="width: 50%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">50%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">平台佣金</span>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 mr-3">
                  <div class="bg-red-500 h-3 rounded-full" style="width: 20%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">20%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">人工报价成本</span>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 mr-3">
                  <div class="bg-orange-500 h-3 rounded-full" style="width: 15%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">15%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">质量损耗</span>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 mr-3">
                  <div class="bg-red-400 h-3 rounded-full" style="width: 10%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">10%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">管理运营</span>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 mr-3">
                  <div class="bg-gray-500 h-3 rounded-full" style="width: 5%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">5%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-red-100 rounded-xl">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600">100%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-red-700">传统模式总成本</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Geppetto成本结构 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-blue-50 rounded-3xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">Geppetto成本结构</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">智能制造成本</span>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 mr-3">
                  <div class="bg-blue-500 h-3 rounded-full" style="width: 40%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">40%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">AI技术成本</span>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 mr-3">
                  <div class="bg-purple-500 h-3 rounded-full" style="width: 5%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">5%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">质量保证</span>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3 mr-3">
                  <div class="bg-green-500 h-3 rounded-full" style="width: 3%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">3%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">运营支持</span>
